{
  "stem": "6195.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So all the passengers started laughing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They said, it's only an exercise.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And a policeman came on the tram.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he said, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It's not an exercise.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We are at war with Germany.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were invaded this morning.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was 1st of September, and we still laughed it off.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't want to get off the tram.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they were quite [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] adamant about it, that we have to get out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were no shelters.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had to just go into the first building there was that was the closest.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it looked serious, no people in the streets, everybody off the street.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And, and inside, I hoped that I am wrong-- that I am right, I mean, that it's only [BACKGROUND NOISE] an exercise.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] well, it was serious.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then I started worrying about my parents.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I wanted to be at home with my parents, with my brother, with my sister.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I didn't want to-- if it's war, then you don't want to be away from them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we were told that-- only when the sirens stopped, that-- luckily enough, I was about two stops from my home.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I quickly got later on the tram and got home.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Well, it didn't take long, two days or three days.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I remember that on the radio, there was the rabbi of Cracow and the archbishop of Cracow saying prayers and assuring us, everybody, the residents of Cracow, that Cracow, no matter what, won't be touched by, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] by the war, and no building will be destroyed.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "This stuck in my mind, really.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And they, they were right, of course.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
